<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٣٧٩ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(حم)</span> : <span class="c1">" مَنْ رَآنِي فَقَدْ رَأَى الْحَقَّ , فَإِنَّ الشَّيْطَانَ لا يَتَكَوَّنُ بِي "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">أَحْمَدُ:</span> ثنا هَارُونُ , بِإِسْنَادِ الَّذِي قَبْلَهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>